<ab><lb n="1"/> <persName type="divine"><persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#Ἄθικτος">Ἀθίκτῳ</name></persName></persName> <w lemma="ἥρως">ἥρωι</w> <lb n="2"/> <w lemma="ὁ">ἡ</w> <w lemma="γυνή">γυνὴ</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὰ</w> <lb n="3"/> <w lemma="τέκνον">τέκνα</w> <w lemma="μνήμη">μνή<lb n="4" break="no"/>μης</w> <w lemma="χάρις">χάριν</w> <lb n="5"/>  <g ref="#leaf"/>  </ab>
</div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To Athiktos, hero, his wife and his children, in memory.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Reinach comments that the name is only known in Latin.</p>
         </div>
